@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
actor Browser
node Frontend
cloud Backend
database CloudSQL
cloud Prometheus
cloud GrafanaCloud
cloud CloudLogging

Browser -> Frontend : page requests, metrics push (/api/metrics)
Frontend -> Backend : REST calls
Backend -> Prometheus : /actuator/prometheus (scrape)
Prometheus -> GrafanaCloud : remote_write
Backend -> CloudLogging : structured logs (logback -> cloud logging)
CloudLogging -> GrafanaCloud : logs-based metrics

@enduml